OL,7,FScottish Borders Council has released
OL,8,Fits proposals for cuts and closures of
OL,9,Fsports, leisure and cultural
OL,10,Ffacilities, as part of a plan to save
OL,11,F#2million from the running costs of
OL,12,FLive Borders.
OL,14,FThe report was due to be released on
OL,15,FThursday, 13 November, but its
OL,16,Fpublication was delayed until Friday
OL,17,Fafternoon.
