OL,3,CFate of leisure facilities and
OL,4,Ccommunity centres in the Borders
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FBy March 2029 at the very latest, Live
OL,8,FBorders will have a much smaller
OL,9,Frepertoire - during this 'transitional
OL,10,Fperiod' the trust - along with
OL,11,FScottish Borders Council - is going to
OL,12,Fbe working with communities to see how
OL,13,Fit can off load a number of community
OL,14,Fspaces.
OL,16,FGala's Focus Centre and St Ronan's
OL,17,FWells in Innerleithen are among those
OL,18,Fset for immediate closure.
