OL,4,Ccommunity centres in the Borders
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FDozens of others have been suggested
OL,8,Ffor community asset transfer - but
OL,9,Fthere's no guarantee that communities
OL,10,Fwill have the desire, or the means, to
OL,11,Ftake them on.
OL,13,FIf no alternative for these places are
OL,14,Fsought by 2029, they too will close.
OL,16,FThe plans will be discussed and final
OL,17,Fdecisions made in a special council
OL,18,Fmeeting on Thursday 20 November.
