OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FUp to #5.3million will be provided in
OL,8,Fcapital investment, subject to
OL,9,Ffeasibility studies.
OL,11,FLive Borders will be provided with
OL,12,Fadditional funding of #1.322m in 2026/
OL,13,F27, #0.156m in 2027/28 and #0.028m in
OL,14,F2028/29, subject to final budget
OL,15,Fapproval.
OL,17,FThe Council has agreed to incur costs
OL,18,Fof #101k as a result of the proposals.
