OL,7,FThe repayment of a previously approved
OL,8,F#1m loan will be delayed until the
OL,9,FLive Borders Business Transformation
OL,10,Fprogramme is complete.
OL,12,FCouncil leader Euan Jardine said: "The
OL,13,FJoint Transformational Change
OL,14,FProgramme has already delivered a lot,
OL,15,Fbut with continued financial pressures
OL,16,Fwe must do more, or we put at risk the
OL,17,Ffuture of all the valued services that
OL,18,FLive Borders provides.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
