OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,F"There is simply not enough money to
OL,8,Fmaintain the status quo, where income
OL,9,Fis too low and operating costs are too
OL,10,Fhigh."
OL,12,FBill Douglas, Chair of Live Borders'
OL,13,FBoard of Trustees, said: "I think it
OL,14,Fis clear from the breadth of
OL,15,Frecommendations developed that we have
OL,16,Flistened to our communities and that,
OL,17,Fwherever possible, we've tried to
OL,18,Fpreserve facilities and services.
